highlights.text: Tobias Sten has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Fy faen du e deili” is the highest at #5.
“Gravemaskinsangen” by Professor Twinkleton Norsk is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #153.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 395 days straight.
“Apocalypse” by Cigarettes After Sex is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 67 spots at #93.
